{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_10","type":"command_execution","command":"/bin/bash -lc 'cat /home/hugo/projects/python-benchmark/results/opencode-deepseek_v4_flash_ollama_cloud/project/README.md'","aggregated_output":"# Chat — Ollama-powered ChatGPT-style SPA\n\nA minimal ChatGPT-like chat interface powered by a local [Ollama](https://ollama.com) server.\nUses **Django Channels** for WebSocket streaming, **LangChain Ollama** for model inference,\n**Tailwind CSS v4** for styling, and **vanilla JS** for real-time DOM updates.\n\n## Prerequisites\n\n- Python 3.14+\n- [Ollama](https://ollama.com) running locally (or on `OLLAMA_HOST`)\n- Node.js (for Tailwind CSS build)\n\n## Quick start\n\n```bash\n# 1. Pull a model (if not already done)\nollama pull qwen2.5:7b\n\n# 2. Set up the environment\ncp .env.example .env\n# Edit .env to set a real DJANGO_SECRET_KEY:\n#   DJANGO_SECRET_KEY=$(openssl rand -hex 32)\nexport DJANGO_SECRET_KEY=\"your-generated-key\"\n\n# 3. Install Python dependencies\npip install .[dev]\n\n# 4. Install Tailwind and build CSS\nnpm ci\nnpx @tailwindcss/cli -i static/css/input.css -o static/css/output.css\n\n# 5. Run the ASGI server\ndaphne -b 0.0.0.0 -p 8000 config.asgi:application\n```\n\nOpen http://localhost:8000 in your browser.\n\n## Environment variables\n\n| Variable | Default | Description |\n|---|---|---|\n| `OLLAMA_HOST` | `http://localhost:11434` | Ollama server URL |\n| `OLLAMA_MODEL` | `qwen2.5:7b` | Model name to query |\n| `DJANGO_SECRET_KEY` | *(required)* | Django secret key |\n| `DJANGO_DEBUG` | `false` | Enable debug mode |\n| `DJANGO_ALLOWED_HOSTS` | `localhost,127.0.0.1` | Comma-separated allowed hosts |\n\n`OLLAMA_HOST` and `OLLAMA_MODEL` are **not** secrets but must be env-driven.\n`DJANGO_SECRET_KEY` is required — generate one with `openssl rand -hex 32`.\n\n## Run with Docker Compose\n\n```bash\nexport DJANGO_SECRET_KEY=$(openssl rand -hex 32)\ndocker compose up --build\n```\n\nThe container expects an Ollama server reachable at `OLLAMA_HOST`\n(defaults to `http://host.docker.internal:11434` inside Docker).\n\n## Run tests\n\n```bash\npytest\n```\n\n## Lint & security\n\n```bash\nruff check .\nruff format --check .\nmypy config/ chat/\nbandit -r config/ chat/\ncoverage run -m pytest\ncoverage report\npip-audit\n```\n\n## Project structure\n\n```\n├── chat/                 # Django app\n│   ├── consumers.py      # WebSocket consumer\n│   ├── llm.py            # Ollama / LangChain integration\n│   ├── routing.py        # WebSocket URL routing\n│   ├── urls.py           # HTTP URL routing\n│   └── views.py          # HTTP views\n├── config/               # Django project config\n│   ├── asgi.py           # ASGI application (HTTP + WebSocket)\n│   ├── settings.py       # Settings\n│   └── urls.py           # Root URL config\n├── static/               # Static assets\n│   ├── css/              # Tailwind input/output\n│   └── js/               # Vanilla JS chat client\n├── templates/            # Django templates\n│   ├── chat/\n│   │   ├── index.html    # Main SPA page\n│   │   └── _message.html # Message partial\n├── compose.yml           # Docker Compose\n├── Dockerfile            # Docker image\n├── pyproject.toml        # Python project config\n└── .env.example          # Environment variable template\n```\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
